message.text:
𝐘𝐨𝐮𝐫 𝐒𝐦𝐢𝐥𝐞𝐬 𝐌𝐚𝐝𝐞 𝐈𝐭 𝐌𝐚𝐠𝐢𝐜𝐚𝐥-𝐍𝐨𝐰 𝐋𝐞𝐭’𝐬 𝐊𝐞𝐞𝐩 𝐭𝐡𝐞 𝐌𝐚𝐠𝐢𝐜 𝐆𝐨𝐢𝐧𝐠!

Thank you, ITHM Tams, for stopping by, sharing your smiles, and becoming part of our story at the ITHM Student Council booth! 

Every photo, every laugh, every moment spent with you was a reminder of what this council stands for—community, leadership, and joy.

We’re just getting started, and there’s more in store for you in the coming days. So stay tuned, keep that smile on, and let’s continue creating the heartbeat of the ITHM community.

Photos by: Ashley Sunggayan, Enzo Abello

#BidaSmileSaITHM
#TamHunt2025
#CultivatingLimitlessPotential
#ITHMStudentCouncil

message.text:
𝐘𝐨𝐮𝐫 𝐒𝐦𝐢𝐥𝐞𝐬 𝐌𝐚𝐝𝐞 𝐈𝐭 𝐌𝐚𝐠𝐢𝐜𝐚𝐥-𝐍𝐨𝐰 𝐋𝐞𝐭’𝐬 𝐊𝐞𝐞𝐩 𝐭𝐡𝐞 𝐌𝐚𝐠𝐢𝐜 𝐆𝐨𝐢𝐧𝐠!

Thank you, ITHM Tams, for stopping by, sharing your smiles, and becoming part of our story at the ITHM Student Council booth! 

Every photo, every laugh, every moment spent with you was a reminder of what this council stands for—community, leadership, and joy.

We’re just getting started, and there’s more in store for you in the coming days. So stay tuned, keep that smile on, and let’s continue creating the heartbeat of the ITHM community.

Photos by: Ashley Sunggayan, Enzo Abello

#BidaSmileSaITHM
#TamHunt2025
#CultivatingLimitlessPotential
#ITHMStudentCouncil

𝐘𝐨𝐮𝐫 𝐒𝐦𝐢𝐥𝐞𝐬 𝐌𝐚𝐝𝐞 𝐈𝐭 𝐌𝐚𝐠𝐢𝐜𝐚𝐥-𝐍𝐨𝐰 𝐋𝐞𝐭’𝐬 𝐊𝐞𝐞𝐩 𝐭𝐡𝐞 𝐌𝐚𝐠𝐢𝐜 𝐆𝐨𝐢𝐧𝐠!

Thank you, ITHM Tams, for stopping by, sharing your smiles, and becoming part of our story at the ITHM Student Council booth! 

Every photo, every laugh, every moment spent with you was a reminder of what this council stands for—community, leadership, and joy.

We’re just getting started, and there’s more in store for you in the coming days. So stay tuned, keep that smile on, and let’s continue creating the heartbeat of the ITHM community.

Photos by: Ashley Sunggayan, Enzo Abello

message.text:
CHARGE, TAMARAWS, CHARGE TO LUNETA! ✊️

Inaanyayahin namin lahat ng mga Tamaraw na sawa na sa korapsyon ng gobyerno na sumali sa mga susunod na pagkilos. Mga kabataan, tayo ang pag asa ng bayan, at makakamit lamang ang mapayapang kinabukasan sa ating pagkakaisa. 

Gamitin ang galit sa korapsyon para baguhin ang mundo!

Bukas, Setyembre 19, ay may gaganaping Black Friday Protest: 
4:00 pm - Assembly @ P. Noval
5:00 pm - March to FEU Gate 4, then Program

Sa Setyembre 21 naman, narito ang programa: 
8:00 am - Assembly of One Ubelt @ Kartilya ng Katipunan
9:00 am - March to Luneta 

I-scan lang ang QR code sa picture upang makasali! 

#MarcosSingilinDutertePanagutin
#NotoCorruption
#Luneta

message.text:
CHARGE, TAMARAWS, CHARGE TO LUNETA! ✊️

Inaanyayahin namin lahat ng mga Tamaraw na sawa na sa korapsyon ng gobyerno na sumali sa mga susunod na pagkilos. Mga kabataan, tayo ang pag asa ng bayan, at makakamit lamang ang mapayapang kinabukasan sa ating pagkakaisa. 

Gamitin ang galit sa korapsyon para baguhin ang mundo!

Bukas, Setyembre 19, ay may gaganaping Black Friday Protest: 
4:00 pm - Assembly @ P. Noval
5:00 pm - March to FEU Gate 4, then Program

Sa Setyembre 21 naman, narito ang programa: 
8:00 am - Assembly of One Ubelt @ Kartilya ng Katipunan
9:00 am - March to Luneta 

I-scan lang ang QR code sa picture upang makasali! 

#MarcosSingilinDutertePanagutin
#NotoCorruption
#Luneta
